    Contexed, Visitor

    public class QuoteVisitor
extends PrefixVisitor<TextMailBuilder>
    Class to convert a Message into a quoted text string Nested messaged are quoted to the appropriate message depth. non text parts are ommitted. If the top level part passed to the visit class is not a message the top level will be unquoted.
